{"tid":1818483,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"要出校園白色恐佈報導 各位巴絲幫幫手","createTime":"2020-01-10T02:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T03:25:11.000Z","uid":218483,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"655a9327dfa430b68a6b77d115b5b47a0938c633","tid":1818483,"uid":218483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T02:56:41.000Z","msg":"小弟要出一篇有關校園白色恐佈嘅報導，而家想搵d被審查or被捕老師做採訪。知道受訪者需要保護，所以一定唔會出名出樣可以放心。而家校園白色恐佈越黎越犀利，小弟真係好希望可以做到一篇好嘅報導，講多d受到無理打壓老師嘅事出黎。如果你身邊有依d人，麻煩幫小弟問下願唔願意將自己嘅故事講出黎。<br />\nTg：@MsDeer<br />\n歡迎隨時聯絡，可以的話唔該各位巴絲幫我推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7643367051c633f756711fd31191b9a3d2cc48f6","tid":1818483,"uid":195248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T02:57:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HoMh1VC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHoMh1VC.jpg&h=6b6d87e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9d046dd13cff6f0774dcf844035258434aa72ab","tid":1818483,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T02:58:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8dff9918f347d2bdce30371cde65a671da94c72c","tid":1818483,"uid":218483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T02:59:24.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"592b2543cb22da411190f0f7b928993501bbd58d","tid":1818483,"uid":218483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T02:59:48.000Z","msg":"自推x1"},{"pid":"effa65141340e6ade03e63a93a9e8bfcacf650cf","tid":1818483,"uid":218483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:00:01.000Z","msg":"自推x2"},{"pid":"11ec16a056ec705794ecb6d20900565f6c369718","tid":1818483,"uid":218483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:00:14.000Z","msg":"自推x3"},{"pid":"9a70c2fc52e330f5c285acc5fa80b1f83caafdc7","tid"